Description: Provides a lightweight R interface to the Ipopt nonlinear
    optimization solver through Ipopt's C interface. The package is intended
    for r-universe builds that provide Ipopt and its open linear solver
    dependencies, such as MUMPS, through system libraries discoverable by
    pkg-config.
License: EPL
Encoding: UTF-8
